cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "Any use of this repository — research, derivative components, downstream software, internal tooling, or production deployments — requires citation as described below. This citation requirement applies in addition to the obligations of the GNU GPL v3 and stands independent of them. A DOI will be added to this file once a Zenodo release is minted."
title: "AI4RA Prompt Library"
abstract: "Versioned, LLM-agnostic prompts, skills, and agents for research administration tasks (RFP extraction, award-notice parsing, document classification, sponsor-default checklists, and related components), with evaluation fixtures and a canonical-source-to-wrappers generation model."
type: software
authors:
